name: Black lampwork with colorful bumps earrings
description:
he lampwork beads used for these earrings are so bright and funky. They are bright black with yellow, purple, light blue and burgundy red bumps. They are complemented with Tibet silver and yellow Swarovski cristals.

Note that Tibet silver is not real silver, but an alloy of metals. I always make sure there is no lead and nickel in the findings that I use for my jewelry. Ear wires are also lead and nickel free and will not cause any allergy. The length of the earrings without ear wires is 2.5 cm or 1 inch. They will certainly not be left unnoticed. A true eye-catcher!
